    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in good condition, well-suited for a daily driver or a family car. The exterior is in great shape, retaining a deep gloss, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from normal use. Mechanically, it has been well-maintained and runs smoothly, with a clean service history and no major issues. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, this is a solid, reliable car that has many miles of life left in it.",
      "price": 33500.0,
