      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person! \ud83d\ude97 I've babied this car since day one, and it's in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that wonderful new-car feel. If you're looking for something that's been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one! I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel\u2014come by and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
