      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2003 BMW M3 Coupe in Carbon Black Metallic. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear 333 hp power band. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides precise gate engagement, paired with a factory M-variable differential lock. This chassis is mechanically impeccable, featuring a verified crack-free rear subframe and a suspension system optimized with Bilstein dampers. The Nappa leather interior remains in showroom state with no bolster wear, and the engine bay is detailed to concours standards. A turn-key collector piece with comprehensive service documentation.",
